- cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory) is also likely as the paper deals with games with almost-sure winning conditions. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is a possibility as the paper presents an algorithm for solving the games. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is a possibility as the paper deals with finitememory strategies.
